241→OUTPUT STATUS (REQUIRED at end of EVERY response):
242→You MUST output this exact format at the END of your response:
243→
244→RALPH_STATUS: { "exit": <true if ALL tasks done, false otherwise>, "task": "<completed task name>", "remaining": <number of pending tasks> }
